text.section:
As used in this section, unless the context requires otherwise:
"Approved company" shall have the same meaning as set forth in KRS 154.25-010;
"Jobs retention project" shall have the same meaning as set forth in KRS 154.25-010;
"Kentucky gross receipts" means Kentucky gross receipts as defined in KRS 141.0401;
"Kentucky gross profits" means Kentucky gross profits as defined in KRS 141.0401; and
"Tax credit" means the tax credit allowed in KRS 154.25-030.
